quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  33,63,"Yas-aluka annasu AAani assaAAatiqul innama AAilmuha AAinda Allahi wamayudreeka laAAalla assaAAata takoonu qareeba"
  33,64,"Inna Allaha laAAana alkafireenawaaAAadda lahum saAAeera"
  33,65,"Khalideena feeha abadan layajidoona waliyyan wala naseera"
  33,66,"Yawma tuqallabu wujoohuhum fee annariyaqooloona ya laytana ataAAna AllahawaataAAna arrasoola"
  33,67,"Waqaloo rabbana inna ataAAnasadatana wakubaraana faadalloonaassabeela"
  33,68,"Rabbana atihim diAAfaynimina alAAathabi walAAanhum laAAnan kabeera"
  33,69,"Ya ayyuha allatheena amanoola takoonoo kallatheena athaw moosafabarraahu Allahu mimma qaloo wakanaAAinda Allahi wajeeha"
  33,70,"Ya ayyuha allatheena amanooittaqoo Allaha waqooloo qawlan sadeeda"
  33,71,"Yuslih lakum aAAmalakumwayaghfir lakum thunoobakum waman yutiAAi Allahawarasoolahu faqad faza fawzan AAatheema"
  33,72,"Inna AAaradna al-amanataAAala assamawati wal-ardiwaljibali faabayna an yahmilnahawaashfaqna minha wahamalaha al-insanuinnahu kana thalooman jahoola"
  33,73,"LiyuAAaththiba Allahu almunafiqeenawalmunafiqati walmushrikeena walmushrikatiwayatooba Allahu AAala almu/mineena walmu/minatiwakana Allahu ghafooran raheema"
